column4: Welcome, you are now talking to an AI doctor. As I am part of a scientific experiment, I would appreciate it if you could take the time to answer a super short questionnaire at the end of the interview. Tap Speak to ask your question and then tap Send to submit it to me.
Hello, how can I help you?
I'm sorry to hear that. Can you tell me the symptoms you are experiencing? That would help me to make a better assessment.

That is not a symptom of a medical condition. However, consuming alcohol can lead to dehydration and electrolyte imbalances, which can cause nausea and headaches. It's important to drink plenty of fluids and rest to help your body recover.
